  "3013400": {
    "name": "Legends of the Round Table Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3013400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/6412c25387adde75f2bb5cb1f7f4edee.avif?t=1771949096\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >试玩内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Legends of the Round Table》的 Demo 版本中体验初次冒险之旅。Experience one of the adventures in this demo of Legends of the Round Table.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/a6f071beaf8b0f0e219b33df7f205d2f.avif?t=1771949096\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/9cce75d31fb1a85da5f15d307b1d4c51.poster.avif?t=1771949096\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/9cce75d31fb1a85da5f15d307b1d4c51.webm?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/9cce75d31fb1a85da5f15d307b1d4c51.mp4?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Legends of the Round Table》，了解于骑士身份在遥远中世纪的真正意义。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >率领圆桌骑士走过亚瑟王波澜壮阔的史诗之路，一同遨游这款充满荣耀、魔法与浪漫的真实中世纪 RPG！在本次 demo 中，你将体验到游戏的首个冒险章节，即亚瑟的成王之旅。游戏的其他冒险故事正如 demo 一样，均改编自真实中世纪故事。每个故事均附带泥金装饰手抄本风格的手绘美术，配合自真实十三世纪作品改编而来的音乐与诗歌，并使用符合时代背景的乐器演奏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/ce6da2af15cf86a70f98d093c137005a.avif?t=1771949096\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/6f290880dbf5d525795afccd5b28fefd.poster.avif?t=1771949096\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/6f290880dbf5d525795afccd5b28fefd.webm?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/6f290880dbf5d525795afccd5b28fefd.mp4?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的视觉灵感源自13世纪的饰边手稿，故事的舞台由中世纪专家采用真实的中世纪绘画技法手绘而成，忠实再现了当时可用的工具、染料和色彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/1821e6fd2b6a1d5391b97c1bc79253b2.avif?t=1771949096\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/9d9f1e3afe6a32e7f55bb07b69263a6d.poster.avif?t=1771949096\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/9d9f1e3afe6a32e7f55bb07b69263a6d.webm?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/9d9f1e3afe6a32e7f55bb07b69263a6d.mp4?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >初次冒险故事既有阴谋与冲突，又伴随着神秘和爱情。你所做的每个决定，无论是放战败的对手一条生路、判决罪犯死刑，还是沉迷于情爱，都会影响到你个人的名望以及王国的未来</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/46c6414c19c47686b122cb0214fac5f6.avif?t=1771949096\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/39077d49a204a9956b9a80d7b807d36a.poster.avif?t=1771949096\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/39077d49a204a9956b9a80d7b807d36a.webm?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/39077d49a204a9956b9a80d7b807d36a.mp4?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >执长枪骑马冲锋、从侍从手中接过备用武器、俘虏敌人索取赎金，光荣的决斗和致命的遭遇都是我们回合制策略战斗系统的支柱。每一场战斗都至关重要，一旦死亡便不可挽回。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/718a21cac3a70f72c8609f2c5ab70c1b.avif?t=1771949096\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/d942f472dd054ce81056a5e92e037b54.poster.avif?t=1771949096\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/d942f472dd054ce81056a5e92e037b54.webm?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/d942f472dd054ce81056a5e92e037b54.mp4?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏音乐均以中世纪乐器演奏，包括鲁特琴、竖琴、维奥尔琴等等。每次冒险都伴以Boston Camerata古乐团著名歌手Anne Azéma演绎的美妙歌曲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/2996222b5986457b532f31288224143f.avif?t=1771949096\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/f54445d33e806e3c6d59f4ba1e9f5170.poster.avif?t=1771949096\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/f54445d33e806e3c6d59f4ba1e9f5170.webm?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/f54445d33e806e3c6d59f4ba1e9f5170.mp4?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理亚瑟王的骑士团，包括兰斯洛特爵士、高文爵士、珀西瓦里爵士等十几位骑士！选择配得上圆桌会议席位的人选，为每个任务指派最适合的骑士，监督他们的职责，从成长、冲突到生命的终结，见证完整的英雄历程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位骑士都独具特色，拥有丰富多样、不断进化的特质，影响着他们应对挑战的方式。他们每一个都拥有自己的欲望、优势、劣势和社交偏好。并非每位骑士都能和其他人相处融洽，团队的凝聚力对他们的成功至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/a1ac0b118bffc3096450cf2aee4f28f6.avif?t=1771949096\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/784066dd2f98dccee6e25d37bca0010e.poster.avif?t=1771949096\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/784066dd2f98dccee6e25d37bca0010e.webm?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013400/extras/784066dd2f98dccee6e25d37bca0010e.mp4?t=1771949096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌系统让玩家成为谱写自己命运的艺术家。您是选择现在就使用圣杯卡牌释放强大的法术来扭转局势，还是留到更加合适的时机？</p>",
